# SECTION VI: CHANGES ALLOWED

  1. Two Decorative potted plants or flowers on the front entrance but not on sills.
  2. Name of resident placed on the mailbox or mail slot.
  3. Holiday lights/decorations on the exterior provided they do not cause holes or other damage. Christmas lights may be installed no earlier than November 1st. All decorations must be removed within two weeks after any holiday.
  4. Any and all flags allowed under United States or Arizona State Statutes.